com.viaoa.util

Class OAXMLReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.util.OAXMLReader

  • public class OAXMLReader
extends java.lang.Object
    OAXMLReader using a SAXParser to parse and automatically create OAObjects from an XML file. This will do the following to find the existing object: 1: if OAProperty.importMatch, then it will search to find a matching object 2: if objectId props, then it will search to find a matching object 3: use guid if not found, then a new object will be created.
    See Also:
    OAXMLWriter
